headline.main: Athletics: Britain's Kilty Retains 60 Meters Title
headline.print_headline: Athletics: Britain's Kilty Retains 60 Meters Title

lead_paragraph: Britain's Richard Kilty overcame a sluggish start to retain his 60 meters title at the European indoor athletics championships on Saturday.
